title: Paquito D'Rivera Workshop: The Art of Teaching and Learning
description: Paquito D’Rivera and the members of his ensemble discuss how much they learn through the process of teaching new generations about Latin and jazz music. For more workshop videos, visit: http://bit.ly/1ucRfj4.
